definitions.title: Def
definitions.body: † [[אֶלְנׇתָן]] (God has given, cf. [[נְתַנְאֵל]], & As. Ilu-iddin Dl:Pr 207, Ph. [[בעליתן]], [[יתנבעל]], Palm. [[עתנתן]], [[והבלת]], Vog:Pal 30 & p. 31 f, Nab. [[והבאל]], [[קסנתן]] Eut:Nab 12:1, Sab. [[והבאל]], [[אלוהב]] DHM:ZMG 1883, 15. 361. 388 CIS:iv. 1, 1.2.6, Theodore, Diodate).

definitions.title: a.
definitions.body: the grandfather of Jehoiakim 2Ki 24:8; cf. Je 26:22, Je 36:12, Je 36:25 (?).

definitions.title: b.
definitions.body: Levites of the time of Ezra Ezr 8:16, Ezr 8:16, Ezr 8:16.
